{"tid":2438730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港黑警同紅色法庭　初選47人　被政權視為性工作者","createTime":"2021-03-08T16:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T16:57:28.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba40ad96456b8fbc60d2cb5e4eaf334791ddd5c1","tid":2438730,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/faningmonisor/posts/10222514536244930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffaningmonisor%2Fposts%2F10222514536244930&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=df6eb661\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/faningmonisor/posts/10222514536244930</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：嚴敏華<br />\n<br />\n香港黑警同紅色法庭，只係把佢哋一向用來對付放蛇捉到的妓女的方式來對付班中產而已。<br />\n根據我在監獄聽到的講法，性工作者被口爆之後，拉到警局裡2-3日不能洗漱，口中散發惡臭地送上庭，之後才是懲教處。<br />\n<br />\n也就是說，47名社會賢達，被這政權視為最低賤的存在。<br />\n沒有鏗鏘地否定紅色法庭的合法性，反而哭訴要求保釋，只是在削減自己僅餘的光環，是致命的政治錯誤。"},{"pid":"945deb77e885525439a5e013fecc1e1bc8adf5c8","tid":2438730,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:51:40.000Z","msg":"我哋又唔係佢地本人 講梗係容易㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770d2bf3878fa13ae65f37681d05efa9eb01d926","tid":2438730,"uid":94314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"945deb77e885525439a5e013fecc1e1bc8adf5c8","tid":2438730,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:51:40.000Z","msg":"我哋又唔係佢地本人 講梗係容易㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同感<br />\n何必仲要加多腳傷害d受害者"}]}